{"title_page": "Mujahidabad", "text_new": "'''Mujahidabad''' ({{lang-ur| \u0645\u062c\u0627\u06c1\u062f \u0622\u0628\u0627\u062f }}) is a neighbourhood in the [[Orangi Town]] borough of [[Karachi]], [[Pakistan]].<ref>[http://www.karachicity.gov.pk/town/index.asp?txtTown=Orangi Orangi Town - Government of Karachi] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060613010717/http://www.karachicity.gov.pk/town/index.asp?txtTown=Orangi |date=2006-06-13 }}</ref>\n\nThere are several ethnic groups in Mujahidabad including [[Muhajir (Pakistan)|Muhajirs]], [[Sindhi people|Sindhis]], [[Kashmiri people|Kashmiris]], [[Saraiki people|Seraikis]], [[Pashtun people|Pakhtuns]], [[Baloch people|Balochis]], [[Memon people|Memons]], [[Musta'li|Bohras]],  [[Ismaili people|Ismailis]], etc.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.karachicity.gov.pk/ Karachi Website]\n\n{{Neighbourhoods of Karachi}}\n\n{{coord|24|56|N|66|57|E|display=title|region:PK_type:city_source:GNS-enwiki}}\n\n[[Category:Neighbourhoods of Karachi]]\n[[Category:Orangi Town]]\n\n{{Karachi-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "'''Mujahidabad''' ({{lang-ur| \u0645\u062c\u0627\u06c1\u062f \u0622\u0628\u0627\u062f }}) is one of the neighbourhoods of [[Orangi Town]] in [[Karachi]], [[Sindh]], [[Pakistan]].<ref>[http://www.karachicity.gov.pk/town/index.asp?txtTown=Orangi Orangi Town - Government of Karachi] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060613010717/http://www.karachicity.gov.pk/town/index.asp?txtTown=Orangi |date=2006-06-13 }}</ref>\n\nThere are several ethnic groups in Mujahidabad including [[Muhajir (Pakistan)|Muhajirs]], [[Sindhi people|Sindhis]], [[Kashmiri people|Kashmiris]], [[Saraiki people|Seraikis]], [[Pashtun people|Pakhtuns]], [[Baloch people|Balochis]], [[Memon people|Memons]], [[Musta'li|Bohras]],  [[Ismaili people|Ismailis]], etc.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.karachicity.gov.pk/ Karachi Website]\n\n{{Neighbourhoods of Karachi}}\n\n{{c